name: THE ELF
description:
My friend and art partner, the elf. Made with paper, wire, ceramics, spray painting, gouache, varnish and digital editing. He was born in 2007, but grew up in 2021.

this beat was made in the 279th session of Beat Brasilis, a pioneer Brasil's beatmakers meeting, which during the pandemic is being online.

sculpture, photography, video and soundtrack by @numadessas at HIC ET NUNC
